fzBlameable
=================

While it is possibe to use clean Doctrine extension blameable, it's possible
that you'll forget to add customized listener to every table that needs Blameable behaviour.
Goal of this plugin is to povide customized Blameable for symfony with back relation alias


Links:
http://botchedcode.com/2010/02/16/symfony-1-4-doctrine-extension-blameable-w-sfguard/
http://www.doctrine-project.org/extension/Blameable